snippet.title: OPEN THE DOOR - Trailer
snippet.description:
OPEN THE DOOR is an indie game by Pilastrum, developed with Visionaire Studio. A graphic adventure game with an old-times-pixel-look. 

Prepare yourself for the simplest adventure ever and OPEN THE DOOR. Get it at http://trumroom.itch.io/openthedoor

In ENGLISH and SPANISH
